  "firstAcquaintance": "Long story short. The princess has entered her rebellious phase and become a bratty princess.",
  "personality": "Her personality has become haughty, constantly flaunting her identity as a princess at all times.",
  "like": "Ketchup",
  "familiarData": "What if Oru Baid were a bratty princess? What would she be like?\nThis is not impossible -- if certain turning points in history had gone differently, this could have been the result.\n\nThe kind and gentle Oru Baid didn't suddenly enter a rebellious phase. While recovering magical artifacts from ancient ruins, she was struck by a certain mirror, causing her counterpart from another world to cross over, putting her into a \"doppelganger\" dual-personality state.\n\nThe girl before you is undeniably Oru Baid -- to be precise, another version of her, an Oru Baid with a different personality and different abilities.\nIn her world, her mother the queen was not by her side. She was raised by a stepmother. The king was away at war, and the stepmother spoiled her excessively, which cultivated her bratty personality.\nHow will the guild master handle this willful and spoiled princess?",
